Its services include ride-hailing, food delivery (Uber Eats), package delivery, couriers, freight transportation, and, through a partnership with Lime, electric bicycle and motorized scooter rental. The company is based in San Francisco, California.
Address: 1455 MARKET ST., 4TH FLOOR, SAN FRANCISCO, CA, US
